<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="attentive-adj">attentive <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'tentɪv/    美 /ə'tentɪv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>专心的；留心的；注意的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They want their children to be <strong>attentive to</strong> their studies.
他们希望自己的孩子用心学习。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>attentively /ə'tentɪvli/ adv   </p></div>